data.title: TeluguMovieNames PDF
data.meta_description: TeluguMovieNames.pdf - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document lists the titles of Telugu films from 1960-1970. There were over 500 films listed from different years within that decade. Some notable or recurring themes in the film titles included religious or mythological stories about figures like Krishna, Rama, and other Hindu gods and goddesses. Many titles also referenced family relationships or dynamics. Overall, the document provides a comprehensive listing of Telugu film titles from a pivotal decade in the Telugu film industry.
